Branches:
	•	latent_8 → final_A
	•	latent_8 → final_B
	•	latent_8 → final_C

So the graph is not linear anymore, it becomes a tree.

That is exactly what your lineage system is designed for.  ￼

⸻

Beast-level insight

Most tools treat diffusion as:

input → output

You are moving toward:

input → trajectory → exploration → outputs

That is a fundamentally better fit for:
	•	local compute
	•	caching
	•	reuse
	•	discovery

⸻

Very concise Beast phrasing

latent step n = real artifact
preview = decode latent n
